     Return a material based on the value k.  k will  be  clamped
     to  be  in the range kmin to kmax.  If kmax < kmin, the null
     material is returned.  The color assigned is an  HLS  color,
     where  H  is  k (mapped to -1,1), L is .5, and S is .9.  The
     hue range is 240.  A suggested gamma value is 0.625.



